<HEADLINE>
<P>
PATRIOTISM, SOCIALISM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Let's see if I have it right. When we send soldiers to be killed or maimed for 
Kuwaiti oil or Haiti soil that's patriotism, but if we ask the rich to give a 
little of their money to help create jobs and for universal health car that's 
socialism. 
</P>
<P>
 MILTON FINKEL 
</P>
<P>
 North Hollywood 
</P>
