<TEXT>
<P>
 * Edward Newquist has been named senior vice president of film production at 
Iwerks Studios, a division of Iwerks Entertainment. Previously, Newquist was a 
vice president of the division. 
</P>
<P>
 Iwerks Entertainment is a Burbank-based developer of specialty movie theaters 
and simulation rides. 
</P>
<P>
 * Douglas Sherrod has been appointed vice president of sales and marketing at 
NBase Switch Communications, a Chatsworth-based company that designs and 
manufactures devices for data communications. Sherrod co-founded Allied Telesis 
Inc., a Mountain View-based manufacturer of local area network phone products. 
</P>
<P>
 * Terry Ann Conrad was named vice president of operations administration at 
Sherman Oaks-based TransWorld Bank. Previously, she was senior vice president 
and chief financial officer at El Segundo First National Bank. * Thomas D. 
Leaper has been appointed chief operating and financial officer of Styles on 
Video Inc., a Canoga Park-based marketer of computer imaging systems. Leaper, 
formerly a partner at Kellogg & Andelson Accounting Corp., will be responsible 
for the company's daily operations under a three-year agreement. 
</P>
