WORLD CUP USA '94: ROUND OF 16; SPOTLIGHT; IT GOES BACK TO CASTRO? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHN-THOR DAHLBERG, Times New Delhi Bureau 
</P>
