<TEXT>
<P>
 Typical confrontation between opposing fans at a World Cup game: 
</P>
<P>
 Brazil follower, in bright green-and-yellow clothing topped by a huge straw 
hat festooned with plastic fruit and vegetables, is roughly grabbed around the 
neck by a U.S. supporter, dressed in red, white and blue, with his face painted 
to resemble the U.S. flag, stars and all. 
</P>
<P>
 The verbal exchange? 
</P>
<P>
 "C'mon pal, one picture. Smile!" EMILIO GARCIA-RUIZ 
