</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070594-0191 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 057816 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 5, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 3; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
